Purge page cache
Editors are encouraged to pick an article from this category and decide whether it satisfies the notability policy.  If not, nominate it for deletion via one of the articles for deletion, speedy deletion or proposed deletion processes.  If you believe the article should be kept, review the text to ensure that it complies with neutral point of view.  After you have made any necessary edits, remove the {{COI}} template. As of 09:53, 7 October 2014 (UTC) the total backlog was 8,314 articles[needs update].
